    "notes": "Route 45 is a very long (20x90 tile) one-way mountain descent from Blackthorn City south to Route 46. The route is defined by repeated ledge sections (L) that force southward one-way travel. Tall grass patches are interspersed throughout. A small lake/pond appears in the center-south section (around rows 42-51) with fishing access for Dratini. The Dark Cave entrance (C) is at the northwest tip (2,5). Sign at (10,4). Trainers are scattered at various depths. Fruit tree at (16,82). Layout is schematic \u2014 actual pokecrystal map has irregular cliff edges and narrow passages."
  },
